most pressing threats now facing NutraSweet, which is made by
a unit of St. Louis-based Monsanto Co. "This is going to give
NutraSweet some real competition," said Mel Wolkstein,
president of Reach Associates, a consulting company based in
South Orange, N.J. "There's likely to be a price war
brewing."
