<HL>
   Who's News:
   Monsanto Taps NutraSweet's Shapiro
   To Lead Agricultural-Products Business
   ----
   By Richard Koenig
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/03/90
